2026-04-05 02:27:02,747 src.chat.session DEBUG Tool call: save_enrichment_protocol({'protocol_yaml': 'name: photo-description-local\ntype: enrichment\nversion: "1"\ncreated: "2026-04-05"\nmaturity: draft\ndescription: Generate photo descriptions and tags locally using BLIP image captioning.\nmedia_types: [photo]\nadapter: shell\ndependencies:\n  pip:\n    - transformers\n    - torch\n    - Pillow\noutput_fields:\n  - description\n  - tags\n  - subject\ncommand: |\n  python3 -c "\n  import sys, json\n  from PIL import Image\n  from transformers import BlipProcessor, BlipForConditionalGeneration\n\n  image_path = sys.argv[1]\n  model_id = \'Salesforce/blip-image-captioning-base\'\n\n  processor = BlipProcessor.from_pretrained(model_id)\n  model = BlipForConditionalGeneration.from_pretrained(model_id)\n\n  image = Image.open(image_path).convert(\'RGB\')\n\n  # Generate unconditional caption\n  inputs = processor(image, return_tensors=\'pt\')\n  output = model.generate(**inputs, max_new_tokens=50)\n  description = processor.decode(output[0], skip_special_tokens=True).strip()\n\n  # Generate guided captions for tags and subject\n  tag_prompt = \'this photo contains\'\n  tag_inputs = processor(image, tag_prompt, return_tensors=\'pt\')\n  tag_output = model.generate(**tag_inputs, max_new_tokens=30)\n  tag_text = processor.decode(tag_output[0], skip_special_tokens=True).strip()\n\n  subject_prompt = \'the subject of this photo is\'\n  subj_inputs = processor(image, subject_prompt, return_tensors=\'pt\')\n  subj_output = model.generate(**subj_inputs, max_new_tokens=15)\n  subject = processor.decode(subj_output[0], skip_special_tokens=True).strip()\n\n  # Parse tags from guided caption\n  tags = [t.strip() for t in tag_text.replace(\'this photo contains\', \'\').replace(\' and \', \', \').split(\',\') if t.strip()]\n\n  print(json.dumps({\n      \'description\': description,\n      \'tags\': tags,\n      \'subject\': subject\n  }))\n  " "{file_path}"'})
